dct_title_s: Follow the Revolution : the route of Washington and the Continental Army, December 25, 1776 to January 6, 1777 [sheet 1]
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Includes directions for following route of Continental Army. Includes facsimile of title cartouche of William Faden's map of 1777.
